            "size": "Large",
            "weight": "Bolder",
            "text": "House passes H.R. 1181 merchant-code ban 221-201 — the first federal gun-bill floor win of the summer heads to the Senate",
            "wrap": true,
            "spacing": "Small"
          },
          {
            "type": "TextBlock",
            "text": "Five Democrats and Kevin Kiley (I) joined 215 Republicans; Fitzpatrick was the lone GOP no. The bill would bar gun-retailer merchant category codes nationwide, pre-empting the CA/CO/NY mandates behind MCC 5723. Also: Sen. Lindsey Graham's death is confirmed via senate.gov.",
            "wrap": true,
            "spacing": "Small"
